          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>At the school carnival, players use tickets to play the games. They win tickets when they are successful in a game. </p><p>Making Purple is a popular game. Red and blue mixed together make purple. To play the game, you spin each spinner once. If you get red on one spinner and blue on the other, you win!</p>"
