        "title": "Text 23",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<ul><li>How often would you expect to get red and blue? How often would you not get red and blue?</li></ul>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "ARAnjWuXGbcF-DU1",
        "title": "Text 25",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>4/18 of the time you would get red and blue or P(red and blue) = 4/18</p><p>14/18 of the time you would not get red and blue or P(not red, blue) = 14/18</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "-laRLmALhP7f8KPe",
        "title": "Text 27",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>The cost to play the game is 2 tickets. The winner gets 6 tickets for making purple. Suppose 36 people play the game. </p><ul><li>How many tickets will the school take in from this game? </li></ul>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "S03oNK-85XDKamdm",
        "title": "Text 29",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>The school will take in 72 tickets from this game. </p><p>Theoretically, they would bring in 2 tickets for each outcome. With 36 trials, there would be double the outcomes.</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
